data.description: Brand New, Never lived in home ready for Immediate Occupancy!! Welcome to the Grand Cayman floor plan built by Ryan in The Groves at New Kent, New Kents newest Age Qualified community!! This home has 3 spacious Bedrooms with ample closet space! The Primary Bedroom features a huge walk in closet and a private Bath with a Shower with a ceramic tile surround and double bowl vanity! The gourmet Kitchen features white cabinets and Island with granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances!! The Kitchen & Dining area has luxury vinyl plank flooring! The Family Room has a comfortable carpeted floor and is open to the Kitchen. The rear, covered patio overlooking protected area is a perfect place to drink your morning coffee!!!
